MooseX-Graph-Easy-StateMachine version 0.01
===========================================

The goodness of Graph-Easy-StateMachine, now with Moose sugar.
Specifically, we call caller()->meta->create with a superclasses
argument instead of just defining an @ISA.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Any::Moose

